### 用户列表（分页 + 筛选）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users?page=1&page_size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 用户列表（按用户名筛选）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users?page=1&page_size=10&username=admin
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 用户列表（按状态筛选 enabled=1, disabled=0）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users?page=1&page_size=10&status=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 获取用户详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 创建用户
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test1234",
  "real_name": "测试用户",
  "phone": "13800138000"
}

### 更新用户
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "updated@example.com",
  "real_name": "新名字",
  "phone": "13900139000",
  "status": 1
}

### 删除用户
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 重置用户密码（管理员）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/2/password
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "NewPass456"
}

### 分配角色给用户
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/2/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role_ids": [1, 2]
}

### 分配门店给用户
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/2/stores
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "store_ids": [1, 2]
}
